@node "reqs" "Requirements"
 You need following things:

        o - Kickstart 3.0 or higher
        o - muimaster.library in version 13 or higher,simply go for the newest
            MUI package
        o - a multisync monitor
        o - many acknowledge and experience with technics of a monitor tube
@endnode

